## Maintenance

- `make docs-check` — verify the docs are internally consistent (also runs on commit).
- `make update` — pull framework improvements from the base without touching your research notes.
<!-- if:SRC_MIRROR_ENABLED=yes -->- `make sync-src` — refresh the `src/` mirror from your workspace.<!-- endif -->
